OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1780931474
OL,3,CPassenger plane makes emergency
OL,4,Clanding after windscreen cracks
OL,6,FAn Aurigny plane had to make an
OL,7,Femergency landing after its windscreen
OL,8,Fcracked during a passenger flight.
OL,10,FThe Guernsey airline confirmed that
OL,11,Fits GR678 service from the island to
OL,12,FManchester, which took off at 5:18pm
OL,13,Fon Sunday 7 June, had to be diverted
OL,14,Fto Southampton Airport following the
OL,15,Fincident.
OL,17,FThe operator has stated that its
OL,18,Fflight crew carried out a
OL,19,F"precautionary emergency landing" in
OL,20,Fline with its standard procedures.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
