PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1780931474
OL,3,CPassenger plane makes emergency
OL,4,Clanding after windscreen cracks
OL,6,FThe flight landed safely and no
OL,7,Fpassengers or crew were injured, with
OL,8,FAurigny arranging a coach to bus
OL,9,Ftravellers from the South Coast to
OL,10,Ftheir intended destination in the
OL,11,FNorth West.
OL,13,FAn alternate aircraft is operating the
OL,14,Fdelayed return GR679 flight from
OL,15,FManchester to Guernsey, which is
OL,16,Fexpected to land around 11:20pm.
